snippet.textDisplay:
Australia has admitted at least 20 other unvaccinated tennis players and athletes on the same grounds as it issued the exemption visa to Djokovic: i.e. that they'd had COVID in the 6-month period before coming to Australia.  

As in all the other cases, Djokovic's application was submitted anonymously and was approved by two sets of evaluators who had no idea whose application they were looking at 

But don't expect WION to tell you any of this.  It specializes in "selective" reporting, after all.
